Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition and language modeling. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with acoustic model training. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a technique to combine inaccurate transcriptions with lattices generated for semi-supervised training. 
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech signal processing. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a technique to improve the performance of speech recognition models.
